               <msContents>
                  <summary>Prayer of Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡, Collection of Asmat Prayers for the days of the Week, Absolution of the Son, ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡, God of the Luminaries, እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘብርሃናት፡, Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡, Supplication of Thanksgiving, ነአኵቶ፡ ለገባሬ፡ ሠናያት፡, Prayer on the Reading of the Epistles of Paul, እግዚአ፡ አእምሮ፡ ወዜናዊ፡ ጥበብ፡, Anaphora of Our Lord, Qǝddase Ǝgzi’, ቅዳሴ፡ እግዚእ፡, Prayer of the Covenant, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡</summary>
